              @issue 261
            @default: 'auto'
          @property max [Number/String]: The maximum value the y axis should show. If set to 'auto' the maximum value will calculated from the data in the series.
            @added: Added an option for setting the maximum y value for a sparkline
              @issue 261
            @default: 'auto'